*---------------------------( Builder : setmsg )-----------------------------*
 
   Type:        command	
   Usage:       setmsg <text>
                
   Description: 'setmsg' is used to, as if you could not guess, set your 
		messages. But what messages? There are four types (currently):
		  magic arrival  -> setmsg mArrive <message>
		  magic leaving  -> setmsg mLeave <message>
                  running        -> setmsg run <message>
                  walking        -> setmsg walk <message>

   Example:     setmsg walk zooms
		(Others see when you move)
		Erikose zooms north.
   
*----------------------------------------------------------------------------*
 See also: 'goto', 'review'
